movie.title: Stonehenge Apocalypse
movie.description_intro: Archeologists come across an Egyptian chamber, causing an electromagnetic pulse, which comes from Stonehenge, that sends destructive shockwaves around the world. When the pyramids are destroyed and the stones start doing strange things; a radio host, a team of scientists, and a team of the British military, try to stop the same force responsible for creating life on Earth, from destroying everything.

movies.title: Caught
movies.summary: The film tells the story of a journalist couple who invite a man and woman into their idyllic village home, but what begins with an informal interview descends into a nightmarish fight for survival.

movies.summary: A group of astronauts living in the haunting emptiness of deep space awake to find earth has suffered an extinction level event.

movies.title: First Man Into Space
movies.summary: Navy test pilot Lieut. Dan Prescott, in experimental rocket plane Y-13, disobeys orders and becomes the first man to fly outside the ionosphere. Unable to turn, he ejects...and is plastered with metallic meteor dust. The pilot compartment lands with no trace of the pilot... but first cattle, then people, are found with their throats cut as if with an axe, by something that seems to have a craving for blood...

movies.title: Justice League vs. Teen Titans
movies.summary: Robin is sent to work with the Teen Titans after his volatile behavior botches up a Justice League mission. The Titans must then step up to face Trigon after he possesses the League and threatens to conquer the world.
